data: In the days of the Second Empire, the Restaurant des Freres-Provencaux still enjoyed a wide renown to which its fifty years of existence had contributed more than a little to heighten its fame.
Massa, Philippe, marquis de, 1831-1911; Ranous, Dora Knowlton, 1859-1916 [Translator]
